  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK826">
<l>naṭṭārpō ṉallavai colliṉu moṭṭārco</l>
<l>lollai yuṇarap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though (one's) foes may utter good things as though they were friends, once will at once understand (their evil, import).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
